[Effect]
Exact Query: The number/barcode must exactly match the input to be queried.
Fuzzy Query: The number/barcode only needs to contain the input to be queried.
Left Fuzzy Query: The latter part of the number/barcode only needs to contain the input to be queried.
Right Fuzzy Query: The former part of the number/barcode only needs to contain the input to be queried.

[Recommendations]
For fuzzy queries, more input leads to more precise results. It is recommended to provide as much input as possible.
